{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59051B0579P0D1N000039", "chronotag": "1739874677829", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CL39", "numeroOrdreDepot": "39", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_LOIS", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59051B0579P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17B0579", "triAmendement": "gaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabh", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA721896", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845514", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": "PA795998"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;Faucillon et Mme&#160;K/Bidi"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 3", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 3", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 3", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0579.asp#D_Article_3"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Supprimer cet article.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Les auteurs de cet amendement souhaitent supprimer l&#x2019;article 3 qui ajoute l&#x2019;activit&#x00E9; professionnelle &#x00E0; la liste des mobiles constitutifs de discriminations afin de punir de trois ans d&#x2019;emprisonnement et de 45&nbsp;000&nbsp;euros d&#x2019;amende les discriminations entravant l&#x2019;exercice d&#x2019;activit&#x00E9;s &#x00E9;conomiques sur le fondement de l&#x2019;activit&#x00E9; professionnelle exerc&#x00E9;e.</p><p>Les auteurs de cet amendement soulignent que l&#x2019;arsenal l&#x00E9;gislatif existant permet d&#x2019;ores et d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; de r&#x00E9;pondre aux actes vis&#x00E9;s par l&#x2019;article 3 et consid&#x00E8;rent donc que les modifications propos&#x00E9;es ne sont pas n&#x00E9;cessaires.</p><p>Ils rel&#x00E8;vent en outre que la notion d&#x2019;&nbsp;&#x00AB;&nbsp;activit&#x00E9; professionnelle&nbsp;exerc&#x00E9;e&nbsp;&#x00BB; comme motifs de discrimination appara&#x00EE;t trop vague et pourrait conduire &#x00E0; des interpr&#x00E9;tations extensives.</p><p>Les auteurs de cet amendement proposent de supprimer cet article afin de maintenir la coh&#x00E9;rence du dispositif l&#x00E9;gal actuel de lutte contre les discriminations.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-01-25", "datePublication": "2025-01-29", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-01-29T16:05:38+01:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59051B0579P0D1N000039?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "75122", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}